---
import '../../style.css';
import '../../enhancements.css';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Not That Deep</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A small tool for right-sizing your reaction." />
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600;9..40,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body data-mode="dismiss">
    <main>
      <header class="site-header"><a class="brand" href="#" aria-label="Not That Deep home">NOT<br />THAT<br /><em>DEEP</em></a><p class="tagline">A reaction-sizing service<br />for the online and internal worlds.</p></header>
      <nav class="mode-switch" aria-label="Choose a mode"><button class="mode active" data-mode="dismiss" type="button"><span>01</span> Dismiss it</button><button class="mode" data-mode="reset" type="button"><span>02</span> Reset</button><button class="mode" data-mode="emergency" type="button"><span>03</span> Emergency</button></nav>
      <section class="panel dismiss-panel" id="dismiss-panel"><div class="eyebrow">Office of Proportion &amp; Perspective</div><h1>Is this worth<br /><span id="time-of-day">your afternoon?</span></h1><p class="intro">Submit the incident for a completely impartial official ruling.</p><label class="sr-only" for="incident">What happened?</label><textarea id="incident" maxlength="220" placeholder="e.g. They replied “interesting” to my very normal post"></textarea><div class="form-row"><span class="character-count"><b id="count">0</b> / 220</span><button id="rule-button" class="primary-button" type="button">Issue ruling <span>→</span></button></div>
        <article class="ruling hidden" id="ruling" aria-live="polite"><div class="ruling-topline"><span>CASE FILE <b id="case-number">NTD–000</b></span><span>STATUS: CLOSED</span></div><div class="ruling-body"><p class="ruling-label">Official finding</p><h2 id="ruling-title">Insufficient grounds for a spiral.</h2><p id="ruling-copy"></p></div><div class="stamp">NOT<br />THAT<br />DEEP</div><footer><span>No further correspondence required.</span><span>Filed today</span></footer><div class="ruling-actions"><button id="share-ruling" type="button">Share ruling</button><button id="download-ruling" type="button">Save image</button><button id="r-rated-button" type="button">Issue R‑Rated Outcome</button></div></article>
        <article class="r-rated hidden" id="r-rated" aria-live="polite"><div class="rr-header"><span>R‑RATED OUTCOME</span><span>PERSONAL DELIVERY</span></div><div class="rr-copy"><p>To whom it may concern:</p><h2 id="rr-title">Please find someone who gives a fuck.</h2><p id="rr-detail">The undersigned has reviewed the situation and has no further emotional resources to allocate.</p></div><div class="rr-seal">SERVED</div><footer><span>Delivered without further discussion.</span><span id="rr-number">RR–000</span></footer><div class="ruling-actions"><button id="share-rr" type="button">Send outcome</button><button id="download-rr" type="button">Save outcome</button></div></article>
      </section>
      <section class="panel reset-panel hidden" id="reset-panel"><div class="reset-heading"><div class="eyebrow">A small interruption</div><h1>Let’s make this<br />a little quieter.</h1><p>Nothing needs to be solved all at once. Give the thought somewhere else to go for a minute.</p></div><label for="spiral">What’s looping? <small>Optional</small></label><input id="spiral" type="text" maxlength="180" placeholder="You can name it, or leave this blank." />
        <div class="release-scene" id="release-scene" aria-live="polite"><div class="river-bank bank-left"></div><div class="river-bank bank-right"></div><div class="river-current"></div><div class="river-thought" id="river-thought"><span id="river-thought-text">A thought can pass through.</span></div><p id="release-caption">When you’re ready, let it drift.</p><button id="release-button" type="button">Let it drift downstream →</button></div>
        <div class="choose-row"><p>Pick what feels doable.</p><button id="surprise-me" type="button">Choose for me ✦</button></div><div class="technique-picker" role="group" aria-label="Choose a grounding technique"><button class="technique selected" data-technique="breathing" type="button"><b>Breathe</b><small>follow a pace</small></button><button class="technique" data-technique="senses" type="button"><b>Notice</b><small>use your senses</small></button><button class="technique" data-technique="defusion" type="button"><b>Unhook</b><small>make some space</small></button><button class="technique" data-technique="category" type="button"><b>Distract</b><small>give your brain a job</small></button><button class="technique" data-technique="reset60" type="button"><b>Reset 60</b><small>one-minute reset</small></button></div><button class="start-reset" id="start-reset" type="button">Start this one <span>→</span></button>
        <section class="exercise hidden" id="exercise" aria-live="polite"><div class="exercise-meta"><span id="exercise-type">PACED BREATHING</span><button id="choose-another" type="button">Choose another</button></div><div id="exercise-content"></div><div class="close-message hidden" id="close-message"><span class="close-mark">✓</span><div><strong>That was a real feeling.</strong><p id="close-copy">You gave it a little less of the whole room. That counts.</p></div></div></section><p class="crisis-line">If this feels like more than a passing spiral, you deserve more support. In Australia, call <a href="https://www.lifeline.org.au/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Lifeline 13 11 14</a>. If you’re in immediate danger, call 000.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="panel emergency-panel hidden" id="emergency-panel"><div class="fire fire-a">✦</div><div class="fire fire-b">✹</div><div class="slimey" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b></b></div><div class="eyebrow">Emergency measures</div><h1>Run out<br />of options?</h1><p>Close the tabs. Step away from the situation. Deploy a trusted person or a small orange worm.</p><div class="emergency-actions"><a class="call-grace" href="tel:0415319229">Call Grace <span>↗</span></a><a class="watch-worm" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82bGfh9hbE0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Watch Slimey the Worm <span>↗</span></a></div><p class="emergency-note">This is the informal emergency line. For a real emergency in Australia, call 000.</p></section>
    </main>
    <script src="../../app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
